/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港發生乜野事<br />\n<br />\n大把稅收, 盈餘下, <br />\n只要撥多d 錢落去MPF 對沖果度, 好快就成事<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾預算案, 搵個無能兼無腦會計佬去做財爺起劏房波</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反而MPF 對沖<br />\n全民退保, 醫保<br />\n勞工假, 銀行假問題<br />\n立法5天工作制<br />\n最高工時<br />\n</span><br />\n呢d 實事, 隨時仲簡單又唔去做, 推都唔撚識推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2蚊乘車, 以前殖民地推既話, 點會由正苦比架<br />\n一定由港督由商界(太古 etc ) 帶頭自己做, <br />\n國泰工會點解咁強大, 都係當年前港英正苦要太古放權<br />\n<br />\n理財新哲學：無條件減利得稅, 免差餉<br />\n<br />\n長遠措施無樣野做到<br />\n有心攪樓市<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">租金管制</span>好應該推動出黎傾下啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門都立法規定<br />\n強制性假日返工要「三工」<br />\n<br />\n香港法例仍然係講緊最少要比員工放勞工假咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民就業<br />\n帶頭無條件減利得稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b740b083a59c58326af6ebe933ccb557c6eae1d0","tid":632916,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18baeada8d5a99db2f04d326b690d4585b77ab49","tid":632916,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf07a3d37d99511b42173a92c1fc115efa92be22","tid":632916,"uid":17765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e9a5302a07e73bbec3a4f2e30efaa20a197e1ad","tid":632916,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d36fd5c8b979c6e0eda7a079d35db4beb7ce053","